'''2008年美國聯盟中區封王決勝加賽'''（也常被稱為'''昏暗之戰'''，{{lang-en|Blackout Game}}）是[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]{{mlby|2008}}賽季的一場{{le|決勝加賽|one-game playoff}}，以決定將由[[芝加哥白襪隊|芝加哥白襪隊]]還是[[明尼蘇達雙城隊|明尼蘇達雙城隊]]在當年的[[美國聯盟|美國聯盟]][[美國聯盟中區|中區]]封王。這場決勝加賽舉行於2008年9月30日的[[美國行動通訊球場|美國行動通訊球場]]（位於[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]）。最終白襪隊靠著[[吉姆·湯米|吉姆·湯米]]的陽春全壘打1比0獲勝，這場比賽[[美國職棒大聯盟決勝加賽列表|大聯盟史上合計得分最低的一場決勝加賽]]。白襪隊之後挺進到[[2008年美國聯盟分區賽|當年的美聯分區賽]]，但他們在那以一勝三敗的成績負於[[坦帕灣光芒隊|坦帕灣光芒隊]]，而雙城隊則是未能晉級季後賽。

進行這場比賽的原因是因為兩隊正規賽季的[[勝率|戰績]]都是88勝74敗。白襪隊季末時贏了一次擲硬幣決定的機會，從而獲得這場比賽的[[主場優勢|主場優勢]]。這場決勝加賽將被作為兩隊正規賽季的第163場比賽，比賽中的各項數據與內容也會算入正規賽季的統計當中。

==背景==
[[Image:2008_MLB_AL_Central_Tiebreaker_Game.JPG|thumb]]，球迷被鼓勵身著黑衣以支持白襪隊]]
{{main|{{le|2008年芝加哥白襪隊球季|2008 Chicago White Sox season}}|{{le|2008年明尼蘇達雙城隊球季|2008 Minnesota Twins season}}}}
[[底特律老虎隊|底特律老虎隊]]和[[克里夫蘭印地安人隊|克里夫蘭印地安人隊]]在前一年的賽季裡是[[美聯中區|美聯中區]]的前兩名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2007.shtml|title=2007 American League Season Summary|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224103942/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2007.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此被[[ESPN|ESPN]]的{{le|湯姆·維爾達奇|Tom Verducci}}及{{le|棒球簡章 (網站)|Baseball Prospectus|棒球簡章}}的{{le|喬·斯漢|Joe Sheehan}}等記者認為是該區本季最強的兩支球隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2008/writers/tom_verducci/03/25/picks.explanation/|title=Season forecast: My playoff picks and surprise teams for '08 campaign|publisher=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|work=SI.CNN.com|date=2008-03-25|first=Tom|last=Verducci|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026132819/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2008/writers/tom_verducci/03/25/picks.explanation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballprospectus.com/article.php?articleid=7285|title=Prospectus Today: AL Preview|first=Joe|last=Sheehan|publisher=Prospectus Entertainment Ventures, LLC|work=[[Baseball_Prospectus|Baseball Prospectus]]|accessdate=2010-05-02|date=2008-03-30|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205756/http://www.baseballprospectus.com/article.php?articleid=7285|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，印地安人隊的陣容飽受傷病困擾<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/fantasy/baseball/flb/story?page=mlbdk2k9_30qindians|title=30 Questions: Can Pronk, V-Mart bounce back?|date=2009-02-26|first=AJ|last=Mass|accessdate=2020-04-11|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502111014/https://www.espn.com/fantasy/baseball/flb/story?page=mlbdk2k9_30qindians|dead-url=no}}</ref>，僅在5月17日前曾佔據過分區第一之位13天<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CLE/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|title=2008 Cleveland Indians Schedule, Box Scores, and Splits|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2017-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320180447/http://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CLE/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 而老虎隊則是從未在美聯中區登頂，最後甚至以14場[[勝差|勝差]]的落後墊底<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/DET/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|title=2008 Detroit Tigers Schedule, Box Scores, and Splits|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814235544/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/DET/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

白襪隊自5月17日追平印地安人隊戰績後，就幾乎都在分區第一的位置，持有該位達154天，甚至即便不在第一時最多也僅落後龍頭一場勝差<ref name="whitesoxseason">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|title=2008 Chicago White Sox Schedule, Box Scores, and Splits|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331165849/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙城隊則是整個賽季大多都在第二名之為追趕白襪隊，期間則曾有54天登頂<ref name="twinsseason">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/MIN/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|title=2008 Minnesota Twins Schedule, Box Scores, and Splits|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101022812/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/MIN/2008-schedule-scores.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管雙城隊九月僅取得11勝15敗，但他們仍在9月25日的{{le|延長局數|extra innings|延長賽}}中擊敗白襪隊，完成兩隊三連戰的橫掃<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280925109|title=Casilla's 10th-inning single gives Twins sweep of ChiSox|date=2008-09-25|accessdate=2020-04-11|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502110958/https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280925109|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙城打完本季最後一場比賽後仍保有分區領先<ref name="twinsseason"/>，迫使白襪隊必須在9月29日的補賽（先前因雨延賽）中與老虎隊對戰以決定是否要再加賽<ref name="rainmakeup">{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280929104|title=Ramirez's grand slam paves way as White Sox force tiebreaker with Twins|date=2008-09-29|accessdate=2020-04-11|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202112510/https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280929104|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這場補賽白襪隊以8比2勝出，使得他們與雙城隊在美聯中區都以88勝74敗並列第一，從而導致必須舉行決勝加賽以決定誰是分區龍頭<ref name="whitesoxseason"/><ref name="twinsseason"/><ref name="rainmakeup"/>。這場決勝加賽的門票在9月29日的補賽結束後一小時內就告售罄<ref name="blackout">{{cite web|url=http://chicago.whitesox.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20080929&content_id=3573972&vkey=pr_cws&fext=.jsp&c_id=cws|title=White Sox tiebreaker game sold out|publisher=MLB.com|date=2008-09-29|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310071138/http://chicago.whitesox.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20080929&content_id=3573972&vkey=pr_cws&fext=.jsp&c_id=cws|archive-date=2012-03-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

白襪隊在九月初的擲硬幣中贏了決勝加賽的主場優勢，因此這場比賽將在[[美國行動通訊球場|美國行動通訊球場]]舉行<ref name="espnpreview">{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/news/story?id=3584515|title=White Sox claim home-field advantage if AL Central comes to tiebreaker|date=2007-09-30|accessdate=2020-04-11|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502111017/https://www.espn.com/mlb/news/story?id=3584515|dead-url=no}}</ref>。球迷被鼓勵身著全黑服裝以展現對白襪隊支持<ref name="blackout"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/05/sports/ncaafootball/05blackout.html|title=When Spotlight Is On, the Clothes Turn Black|last=Branch|first=John|date=2008-10-04|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213054400/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/05/sports/ncaafootball/05blackout.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|TBS美國職棒大聯盟|Major League Baseball on TBS|TBS}}負責這場比賽的轉播<ref name="espnpreview"/>。白襪隊這場比賽推出只休息三天的{{le|約翰·丹克斯|John Danks}}[[先發投手|先發]]，而雙城隊則是派出{{le|尼克·布萊克本|Nick Blackburn}}<ref name="espnpreview"/>。

