雙方的先發投手布萊克本和丹克斯在比賽前期都成功封鎖對方無失分，前四局甚至總共僅六名[[跑壘員|跑者]]上壘<ref name="gamesummary">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA200809300.shtml|title=September 30, 2008 Minnesota Twins at Chicago White Sox Box Score and Play by Play|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001102139/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA200809300.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。五局上半，雙城隊的[[麥克·卡戴爾|麥克·卡戴爾]]一上場就打出二壘安打，然而這也是雙城隊整場唯一一次攻佔得點圈的機會<ref name="gamesummary"/>。丹克斯隨後讓{{le|戴爾蒙·楊|Delmon Young}}擊出深遠飛球被接殺，卡戴爾推進到三壘<ref name="gamesummary"/>。接著，{{le|布蘭登·哈里斯|Brendan Harris}}又擊出一支[[中外野|中外野]]方向的深遠飛球，被白襪隊中外野手[[小肯·葛瑞菲|小肯·葛瑞菲]]接殺出局。卡戴爾此時試圖跑回本壘以變成[[高飛犧牲打|高飛犧牲打]]，但小葛瑞菲精準傳回[[本壘|本壘]]，[[捕手|捕手]]{{le|A·J·皮爾辛斯基|A. J. Pierzynski}}接到球後將卡戴爾阻擋在本壘前，並將其觸殺出局同時結束該半局<ref name="griffgem">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081001&content_id=3577973&vkey=news_cws&fext=.jsp&c_id=cws|title=White Sox marvel at Griffey's throw|first=David|last=Just|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2008-10-01|accessdate=2010-05-02|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023030257/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081001&content_id=3577973&vkey=news_cws&fext=.jsp&c_id=cws|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這個長傳賽後被評為「妙傳（nice throw）」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280930104|title=Danks limits Twins, Thome blasts solo shot as ChiSox clinch playoff berth|date=2008-09-30|accessdate=2020-04-11|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2020-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621092140/https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280930104|dead-url=no}}</ref>及「美技守備（defensive gem）」<ref name="griffgem"/>。

七局下半，白襪隊[[指定打擊|指定打擊]][[吉姆·湯米|吉姆·湯米]]作為該局首名打者擊出陽春[[全壘打|全壘打]]，得到本場比賽唯一的一分<ref name="gamesummary"/>。布萊克本之後讓[[保羅·柯諾可|保羅·柯諾可]]擊出滾地球出局，但被小葛瑞菲打出二壘安打，只好在對{{le|阿列克謝·拉米雷斯|Alexei Ramírez}}{{le|故意四壞保送|Intentional base on balls}}後下場，由[[中繼投手|中繼投手]]{{le|荷西·米亞里斯|José Mijares}}接替投球<ref name="gamesummary"/>。而白襪隊的約翰·丹克斯則投滿八局未失分，第九局則交給[[終結者|終結者]][[巴比·占克斯|巴比·占克斯]]<ref name="gamesummary"/>。最終占克斯完成了三個出局數，拿到本季第30次[[救援成功|救援成功]]，助隊以1比0取勝<ref name="gamesummary"/>。雙城隊中心打線（[[喬·毛厄|喬·毛厄]]、[[賈斯汀·摩爾諾|賈斯汀·摩爾諾]]和卡戴爾）三人生涯對戰丹克斯共計40個[[打數|打數]]22之[[安打|安打]]（[[打擊率|打擊率]]5成50），但這場決勝加賽中卻是9個打數僅1支安打，打擊率僅1成11，還被三振三次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081001&content_id=3577908&vkey=news_cws&fext=.jsp&c_id=cws|title=Danks steps up in tiebreaker|author=Just, David|publisher=MLB.com|date=2008-09-30|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023030301/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081001&content_id=3577908&vkey=news_cws&fext=.jsp&c_id=cws|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這場比賽是大聯盟史上合計最低分的決勝加賽，比先前最低分的{{le|1951年國家聯盟龍頭決勝系列加賽|1951 National League tie-breaker series}}第一戰（3比1）還要少三分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=3617483|title=Tiebreaker Playoff Results|date=2008-09-30|accessdate=2020-04-11|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127173942/https://www.espn.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=3617483|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==後續==
白襪隊獲勝後成功晉級季後賽行列，這是他們自{{wsy|2005}}以來的首次參賽<ref name="franchise">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/|title=Chicago White Sox Team History & Encyclopedia|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2011-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110406112522/http://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但他們在[[2008年美國聯盟分區賽|分區系列賽]]中遭到當年[[2008年世界大賽|世界大賽]]亞軍{{le|2008年坦帕灣光芒隊球季|2008 Tampa Bay Rays season|坦帕灣光芒隊}}擊敗，以一勝三敗告終<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/2008_ALDS2.shtml|title=2008 League Division Series – Tampa Bay Rays over Chicago White Sox (3–1)|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100405222439/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/2008_ALDS2.shtml|archivedate=2010-04-05|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

在[[棒球統計|棒球統計]]上，這場比賽算做正規賽季的第163場比賽<ref>{{cite web |author1=Associated Press |title=Danks limits Twins, Thome blasts solo shot as ChiSox clinch playoff berth |url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280930104 |website=ESPN |accessdate=2020-12-22 |archive-date=2020-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621092140/https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=280930104 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。像是湯米這場比賽的全壘打就是本季第34發，這讓他在聯盟排行榜上並列第四<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2008-batting-leaders.shtml|title=2008 American League Batting Leaders|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2021-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102184958/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2008-batting-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而丹克斯則是在這場比賽後將[[防禦率|防禦率]]從3.47降至3.32，在聯盟排行榜上從並列第十躍升至第五<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2008-pitching-leaders.shtml|title=2008 American League Pitching Leaders|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2021-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102184941/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2008-pitching-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?n1=danksjo01&t=p&year=2008|title=John Danks 2008 Pitching Gamelogs|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221610/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?n1=danksjo01&t=p&year=2008|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙城隊的毛厄、摩爾諾以及白襪隊外野手{{le|卡洛斯·奎丁|Carlos Quentin}}因為他們本季優秀的進攻表現獲得[[銀棒獎|銀棒獎]]<ref name="awards">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2008-other-leaders.shtml|title=2008 American League Awards, All-Stars, & More Leaders|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|accessdate=2010-05-03|archive-date=2017-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731004750/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2008-other-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。毛厄還獲得同年的[[金手套獎|金手套獎]]<ref name="awards"/>。這場決勝加賽將是最後一次由擲硬幣的方式來決定誰是主場。隨著大聯盟在2008年的球季結束後修正了規定，未來決勝加賽的主場優勢，將由雙方在季賽中相互對戰成績較佳者獲得<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/content/printer_friendly/mlb/y2009/m01/d15/c3745318.jsp|title=Ownership approves two major rules amendments|date=2009-01-15|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]|accessdate=2020-12-22|archive-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312090411/http://mlb.mlb.com/content/printer_friendly/mlb/y2009/m01/d15/c3745318.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

